             was indicted for <rs id="t18180617-98-off545" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18180617-98-off545" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180617-98-off545" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18180617-98-cd546" type="crimeDate">20th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180617-98-off545 t18180617-98-cd546"></join>, at St. Andrew Undershaft, thirty yards of kerseymere, value 10l., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18180617-98-victim852" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Simpson
                        <interp inst="t18180617-98-victim852" type="surname" value="Simpson"></interp>
